data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED,! NEED CLOSING COST ASSISTANCE, WANT A RATE BUY DOWN, WANT A CREDIT FOR UPDATES? BRING YOUR IDEAS & LETS TALK!  Check out this beautiful 4 bed/2.5 bath home nestled in center of cul de sac w/2 car garage & fenced yard w/lrg shed! Open, flowing floor plan. The front room is a large multipurpose room, the possibilities are endless! First level flooring was replaced in 2022 with gorgeous LVP! Cabinets (not drawers) are soft close, new counters/backsplash are quartz. Fantastic appl pkg, dble tap fridge door to see what's insikes round iceballs! Oven is also covection oven & air fryer. Multi colored under cabinet lighting can be controlled thru your phone to create a super cool vibe! New faucet/hardware. Kitchen opens to eat-in kitchen & den w/gas fireplace. Upstairs is a HUGE primary bed w/LARGE bath & HUGE WIC! 3 addl beds all w/WIC! Laundry rm w/wash/dry that convey! NO ASSOCIATION.
